name: Abunai Houkago: Mou Matenai
overview:
Released in March 1989.

The title of this game translates from Japanese as 'Look Out! After School - I Can't Wait Any More'.

A hanafuda game.

Abunai Houkago - Mou Matenai is a Strategy game, developed and published by Green Soft, which was released in Japan in 1989.
